info.name: Roxy Armchair
info.description: Transform your lounge into a vintage boudoir setting with this gorgeous Roxy armchair. Showcasing a fabulous burgundy fabric finish, it's just the piece to add drama to your room. The Roxy armchair features a deep tub shape that offers style and comfort. Featuring top quality construction, the Roxy armchair is crafted in Australia with a pine timber frame.
